{
  "stem": "23131.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he came-- he decided one time, he had so much complaints about that they were eating, were not doing nothing, that Tuvia does this, that [?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Tuvia does ?] that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he called Tuvia one time and another time, and he tried to explain to him that it's not so.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he said, you know what-- he said to him, you know what?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You come to the base and take a look for yourself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and then you maybe all your answer-- questions will be answered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It took a while, but he did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh, we received him beautifully.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He went-- he couldn't get over it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He couldn't get over the kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He couldn't get over the-- the workshops.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He couldn't get over nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] in camp where leather was in a big pail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What did they-- what did they use the leather for?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Repairing shoes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they used to put the leather in water, and I don't know how they did it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it was-- at the-- and they-- they had a lot of use of the leather, what they-- sometimes they used to make a pair of boots, a pair of shoes.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this was a very big barrack for the leather.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was pretty smelly because leather smells.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there, they used to come, for [NON-ENGLISH], for the holidays.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the shochet was on top of them all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sure enough, Platon walked in there and looked and wondered how-- how are they making the leather, how are this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He couldn't-- he couldn't believe his eyes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, what are you doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those people that are saying and-- and all the time [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So Tuvia was afraid to tell him that they are davening.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
